mosais.distribution

Class BoundingBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • mosais.distribution.BoundingBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNodeModel

    public class BoundingBox
extends java.lang.Object
implements TreeNodeModel
    An area in a coordinate plane. The area is defined by the point in the top left corner plus the width and height.
    Author:
    Andrew Trismen
